v1.1.2 Phase 72 (2026.7.12, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - chess.src/ui.js (GPL v3): _reviewAnalyzeAdvance — fixed "false
    completion" bug after long-press priority eval. The completion check
    now scans the ENTIRE range [0.._lastStep] for uncached steps (not just
    forward from _reviewAnalyzeStep+1), so a priority eval that jumped
    ahead no longer causes the batch to report completion while earlier
    steps remain un-analyzed.
  - chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.2 Phase 71 (2026.7.11, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - stats.html (GPL v3): CSP switched from 'sha256-<hash>' blob: to
    'unsafe-inline' blob: (fixes the user-reported move-selection bug —
    SHA-256 hash policy blocked all 23 inline onclick handlers per CSP L2+).
    XSS hardening: renderPGNText movetext-walk fallback, variation-text walk,
    and firstMoves opening-plies list now route unrecognized characters
    through _escFEN before HTML insertion (neutralizes malicious PGN
    payloads that would execute under 'unsafe-inline'). Chess960 0-distance
    castling: executeMove adds _isZeroDistKingCastle branch (king stays put,
    only rook moves); buildSAN accepts 0-distance as castling; board-mutation
    block skips king move when from===to.
  - chess.src/ai-bridge.js (GPL v3): uciToCoords attaches castle flag to
    result.to when rewriting Chess960 castling.
  - chess.src/ui.js (GPL v3): executeMove checks to.castle as primary source
    for castle flag.
  - chess.src/game-logic.js (GPL v3): _castleSide 0-distance branch +
    secureRandomInt crypto guard + moveAlg typeof guard + en-passant inB()
    bounds checks.
  - chess.src/chess960.js (AGPL v3): toShredderCastling board guard.
  - chess.src/pgn-standard.js (GPL v3): sevenTagRoster/composePGN null guards.
  - chess.src/worker-pool.js (GPL v3): 3-strike transient-failure counter.
  - chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
  - No new third-party code introduced.

v1.1.2 Phase 70 (2026.7.10, same-version revision):
  - Version remains versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - chess.src/ui.js (GPL v3): _pgnCacheBuildSaveContext edge case fix
    (force-rebuild checks _reviewEvalCache.size > 0, not _inReview).
  - chess.src/game-logic.js (GPL v3): makeMvInPlace inB() bounds check.
  - chess.src/ai-bridge.js (GPL v3): 7 debug console.log removed.
  - chess.src/eco-data.js (AGPL v3): 1 debug console.log removed.
  - chess.html: rebuilt from chess.src/.
