v1.1.2 Phase 67 (2026.7.7):
  - Version bumped to versionCode=112, versionName="1.1.2".
  - chess.src/game-logic.js (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived):
    * P1 fix: makeMv() now validates BOTH from and to coordinates via inB()
      before any board access. Previously only from.row was bounds-checked.
    * Emoji-space fix: 6 i18n keys (stats_title, stats_export_html,
      stats_review, save_pgn_prompt, variation_toggle, pgn_cache_manager)
      now have a space between emoji and following text (zh/en sync).
