      pgn_cache_partial_eval_title, pgn_cache_partial_eval_msg (with
      N1/N2 placeholders for total/cached step counts),
      pgn_cache_partial_eval_analyze_first,
      pgn_cache_partial_eval_save_as_is, pgn_cache_analyze_then_save.
  - chess.src/ai-bridge.js (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived):
    * P2 fix: onHintMove() adds inB() bounds check on coords.from/coords.to
      before board access. Defensive against race conditions.
    * Redundancy cleanup: removed leftover console.log in onBestMove and
      onHintMove (Phase 66 cleanup miss).
  - chess.src/ui.js (GPL v3, DroidFish-derived):
    * Task 67.2 root-cause fix: _pgnCacheSaveCurrentImpl() now checks
      _reviewEvalCache coverage before _buildPGNString; if incomplete AND
      reviewMode AND not pure-import, calls new
      _pgnCacheShowPartialEvalDialog() with 3 options (Analyze All first /
      Save anyway / Cancel). _reviewAnalyzeAdvance() completion path
      triggers deferred save via _pgnCacheSaveCurrentImpl_SkipCoverageCheck().
      _resetGameUIState() and exitReview() clear _pendingPGNCacheSave.
    * Version bump: header badge <span class="ver">v1.1.1</span> → "v1.1.2";
      about dialog "v1.1.1" → "v1.1.2"; render-error page "v1.1.1" → "v1.1.2"
